; ── installer.nsh ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; Custom NSIS include for electron-builder.
; Language is set to en_US (1033) in package.json — MUI2 already provides
; all required LangStrings for English, so no overrides needed here.
; This file is intentionally minimal to avoid compatibility issues with
; the NSIS 3.0.4.x version bundled by electron-builder.
